 Posts: 80<br> <font color=#E09C5F>(6/29/01 9:59:54 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   New PVP server</span><hr size=1> Here is a thread from the new PVP server message board. I am getting more and more interested in this. There really are no rules to this server. The only thing you have to do is not be abusive to another character. They figure if there are any disputes on the server, you have access to ways to settle them yourself. Training is a totally acceptable form of revenge. Honestly though, it does look like a lot of fun for experienced players. It's live now and from what I have read, the highest level person on the server is up to 15 now. <br>
<br>
What are your thoughts on this?<br>
<br>
